English: Permissions at higher levels are Field Level permissions. All Fields have a Permission Level set against them and the rules defined at that permissions apply to the field. This is useful in case you want to hide or make certain field read-only for certain Roles.

Tous les champs ont un ensemble Niveau d'autorisation contre eux et les règles définies à ce autorisations se appliquent sur le terrain.
